    <h2 class="big-title reveal">What to <em>Build It From</em></h2>
    <p class="intro reveal">The material determines how long your bed lasts, whether it's safe for food, and what you'll spend. Here's a full honest comparison with pros, cons, and food safety included.</p>
    <div class="scroll-x reveal">
      <table class="mat-table">
        <thead><tr><th>Material</th><th>Upfront Cost</th><th>Lifespan</th><th>Food Safe</th><th>Notes</th></tr></thead>
